summary: Replaces all craftable and prewar paintings with Suicide Girls
descriptionHtml:
Suicide Girl replacement textures for all the Paintings in game.
Right now I've only done the Craftable Paintings and their Prewar Copies seen throughout the game.

I switched the prewar with generic paintings so the ones you place in your home will look pristine and new, while the ones seen in the world will look distressed.

This is my first mod so please give an endorsement if you like it. I put a lot of work into distressing the images and making sure they all fit the frames, unlike most of the retexture mods I've seen so far so hopefully you like it and will spread it around. I'll have constant updates to add more pictures on all the Billboards and Signs as I get them finished.

[INSTALLATION]

Just drop the {textures} folder into your DATA folder in Fallout 4 and enjoy!
author: Sickotik
